{"TopicId":184279,"ForumId":148,"TopicTitle":"Kerbal Space Program Breaks Ground with a New DLC!","CreatedByName":"UomoCapra","CreatedById":167737,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-06T14:02:49Z","PageNum":17,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"MechBFP","CreatedById":184845,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-07T16:10:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223595000\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557245378\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022192336\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nigel Cardozo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Nigel Cardozo said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat happens to Making History after this update?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat do you mean?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealKerbal3x","CreatedById":183830,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-07T16:10:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223595000\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557245378\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022192336\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nigel Cardozo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Nigel Cardozo said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat happens to Making History after this update?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t think BG is replacing MH in any way. It\u0027s just KSP\u0027s second DLC.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Phoenix84","CreatedById":26027,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-07T16:10:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223595000\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557245378\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022192336\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nigel Cardozo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Nigel Cardozo said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat happens to Making History after this update?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s still available to play, same as now. Not sure what you\u0027re asking.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"VoidCosmos","CreatedById":192336,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-07T16:13:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223595001\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557245434\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022184845\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MechBFP\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, MechBFP said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat do you mean?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWill \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/66485-squad/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002266485\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/66485-squad/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@SQUAD\u003C/a\u003E update Making History after Breaking Ground is released\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RocketBlam","CreatedById":103420,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-07T16:15:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI like this expansion a lot better than the last one. In fact I never even bought the last one because I couldn\u0027t see any situation where I would use any of it. But this looks like it fills out a lot of the shortcomings of the base game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Chryssalid 8492","CreatedById":197332,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-07T16:17:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223595007\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557245625\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022192336\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nigel Cardozo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Nigel Cardozo said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWill \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/66485-squad/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002266485\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/66485-squad/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@SQUAD\u003C/a\u003E update Making History after Breaking Ground is released\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAdding new parts probably not, but tweaking parts and fixing bugs almost certainly.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klesh","CreatedById":110814,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-07T16:17:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223595007\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557245625\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022192336\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nigel Cardozo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, Nigel Cardozo said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWill \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/66485-squad/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002266485\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/66485-squad/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@SQUAD\u003C/a\u003E update Making History after Breaking Ground is released\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLets hope so, there still are a few lingering bugs (that probably got ported into the console version of the parts pack too).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealKerbal3x","CreatedById":183830,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-07T16:19:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223595007\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557245625\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022192336\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nigel Cardozo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, Nigel Cardozo said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWill \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/66485-squad/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002266485\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/66485-squad/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@SQUAD\u003C/a\u003E update Making History after Breaking Ground is released\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOf course they will. As I said above, I don\u2019t think BG is intended to replace MH.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Eskandare","CreatedById":62742,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-07T16:26:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223594982\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557243317\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022110814\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022klesh\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n48 minutes ago, klesh said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSays so right in the \u003Cabbr title=\u00221. Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it. 2. Overpowered. A part or mechanic that upsets game balance by being too powerful.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E, man.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI must have missed that somehow. I\u0027m on mobile right now and\u00A0I\u0027m under something odd tons of steel,\u00A0so not all things display clearly.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pthigrivi","CreatedById":105624,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-07T16:33:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223594604\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557182712\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022105132\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022klgraham1013\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 hours ago, klgraham1013 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTacos.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTacos should be the new SI unit for dollars/(joy*seconds).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xurkitree","CreatedById":187694,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-07T16:39:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWill there be a DLC bundle once this comes out? At a slightly discounted price than buying the two seperately ofcourse. It would make life much easier if I could buy new engines and new science at the same time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223595018\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557246806\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022105624\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Pthigrivi\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, Pthigrivi said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTacos should be the new SI unit for dollars/(joy*seconds).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat\u0027s the unit of Joy?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Angelo Kerman","CreatedById":106975,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-07T17:16:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223594919\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557236860\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022110881\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022KingPhantom\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, KingPhantom said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni hope that all parts are also usable in space... i smell a canadarm on the stations. that would be AWESOME\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah! I might make a version of my Mk1 Station Arm from KerbalActuators, which is currently a programmable single-part robot arm, and turn it into a multi-part robot arm powered by the DLC\u2019s Kerbal Robotics (or whatever it\u2019s called). Speaking of which, here\u2019s hoping that we get a sequencer of some sort. Like, record positions of various servo parts and then play them back. I did that for KA but a DLC powered solution would be one less thing that I have to maintain...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Foxster","CreatedById":113764,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-07T17:27:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223595025\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557247156\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022187694\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Xurkitree\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n47 minutes ago, Xurkitree said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWill there be a DLC bundle once this comes out? At a slightly discounted price than buying the two seperately ofcourse. It would make life much easier if I could buy new engines and new science at the same time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat\u0027s the unit of Joy?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo, it\u0027s not Watts. (This works much better out loud).\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klgraham1013","CreatedById":105132,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-07T17:27:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223594951\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557240471\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289250\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022mindstalker\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, mindstalker said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHumans invented solid state rockets a 1000 years ago. Kerbals just weren\u0027t constrained by concepts like surviveability and oxygen, before strapping themselves above, besides, under a rocket to reach the stars.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYour logic and reason has no place here!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat aside.\u00A0 I think it would be beneficial of Squad to reconsider the tech tree now that moving across the surface of planets may actually have a gameplay function.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"shdwlrd","CreatedById":113880,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-07T17:31:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223595064\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557250063\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022105132\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022klgraham1013\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 minutes ago, klgraham1013 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0I think it would be beneficial of Squad to reconsider the tech tree now that moving across the surface of planets may actually have a gameplay function.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes... this. I would actually play career or science modes if the tech tree was redone.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-05-07T17:33:17Z\u0022 title=\u002205/07/2019 05:33  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EMay 7, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by shdwlrd\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EDerp... mobiles\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klgraham1013","CreatedById":105132,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-07T17:33:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223594994\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557244814\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022125662\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Snark\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Snark said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSorry for the long post...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLet\u0027s be real.\u00A0 This should just be default at the beginning of all your posts.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLove your posts anyway.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223594998\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557245139\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022105624\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Pthigrivi\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Pthigrivi said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is a relatively small but important question and I\u0027d love to know how they\u0027re handling this. The trick with time-based science is you don\u0027t want to let players just put one thing down and time-warp to infinite science, so Im assuming there will be some sort of either diminished returns and/or cutoff. The MPL mechanics are much improved from their earliest implementation but still a little clunky in the UI department. They\u0027ve hinted at adding a lot of dimension to the process of gathering so I certainly hope they\u0027ve been thinking of ways to make it all manageable and streamlining things as much as possible.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere\u0027s been many threads on how KSP could successfully pull off time based mechanics.\u00A0 I\u0027m hoping Squad has read them, as reiterating them would take a long time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pthigrivi","CreatedById":105624,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-07T17:44:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223595025\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557247156\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022187694\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Xurkitree\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Xurkitree said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWill there be a DLC bundle once this comes out? At a slightly discounted price than buying the two seperately ofcourse. It would make life much easier if I could buy new engines and new science at the same time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat\u0027s the unit of Joy?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJoy = 1/fresh-out-of-the-oven\u00A0cookie feelings^2\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-05-07T17:44:59Z\u0022 title=\u002205/07/2019 05:44  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EMay 7, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Pthigrivi\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"PrathamK","CreatedById":176896,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-07T18:01:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n$14.99 it\u0027s around \u20B91043 INR, I got the game at a cheaper price of \u20B9800.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KerballingSmasher","CreatedById":195689,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-07T18:05:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223594148\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557152413\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022193267\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DocMike\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 5/6/2019 at 4:20 AM, DocMike said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022shut_up_and_take_my_money-t2.jpg\u0022 src=\u0022http://hd.wallpaperswide.com/thumbs/shut_up_and_take_my_money-t2.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI WANT THIS, TOO, \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/193267-docmike/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022193267\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/193267-docmike/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@DocMike\u003C/a\u003E!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-05-07T18:06:12Z\u0022 title=\u002205/07/2019 06:06  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EMay 7, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Kerballing (Got Dunked On)\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xurkitree","CreatedById":187694,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-07T18:17:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223595089\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557252064\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022176896\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022PrathamK\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n16 minutes ago, PrathamK said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n$14.99 it\u0027s around \u20B91043 INR, I got the game at a cheaper price of \u20B9800.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes. 40$ turns into less than 15$. Nice to see another Indian here lmao. DLC is like half of that, so is SR2.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-05-07T18:17:37Z\u0022 title=\u002205/07/2019 06:17  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EMay 7, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Xurkitree\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"theonegalen","CreatedById":71012,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-07T18:33:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223594817\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557215421\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u00225thHorseman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, 5thHorseman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn Astroneer you can cut a PLANET in HALF with the terrain deformation tool.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E And really all I\u0027d like in KSP is a way to flatten (to a certain altitude above/below sea level around the center of the planet) an area to make a base.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E And then base building tools so I can land raw materials there and turn them into a \u0022mining module\u0022 or a \u0022habitation module\u0022 or a \u0022construction module\u0022 or a landing pad or a... and all these modules would be one-piece so the entire base is no more than a dozen or so parts, one per module.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/106975-angel-125/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022106975\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/106975-angel-125/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Angel-125\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0has that in his bulldozer part. It works with Kerbal Konstructs, IIRC. It would be nice to have it as part of stock or a DLC though.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EAlthough if KK-lite became part of stock or DLC, \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/167349-ger_space/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022167349\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/167349-ger_space/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Ger_space\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0would probably commit modder sudoku. And that would make me sad.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223595050\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557249374\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022106975\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Angel-125\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Angel-125 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah! I might make a version of my Mk1 Station Arm from KerbalActuators, which is currently a programmable single-part robot arm, and turn it into a multi-part robot arm powered by the DLC\u2019s Kerbal Robotics (or whatever it\u2019s called). Speaking of which, here\u2019s hoping that we get a sequencer of some sort. Like, record positions of various servo parts and then play them back. I did that for KA but a DLC powered solution would be one less thing that I have to maintain...\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSynthesizers aren\u0027t useless without a sequencer, but a sequencer makes them so much more useful!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-05-07T18:34:48Z\u0022 title=\u002205/07/2019 06:34  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EMay 7, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by theonegalen\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klesh","CreatedById":110814,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-07T18:44:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAre you guys planning on having another DLC release livestream featuring Scott Manley?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAre you planning on answering any of the myriad of questions your community is asking in this thread?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-05-07T18:46:12Z\u0022 title=\u002205/07/2019 06:46  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EMay 7, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by klesh\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MechBFP","CreatedById":184845,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-07T18:48:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223595105\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557254697\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022110814\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022klesh\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n21 minutes ago, klesh said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAre you guys planning on having another DLC release livestream featuring Scott Manley?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAre you planning on answering any of the myriad of questions your community is asking in this thread?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey are putting together \u201CKSP Loading\u201D articles. Patience. I am sure many questions will be answered by those.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-05-07T19:06:38Z\u0022 title=\u002205/07/2019 07:06  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EMay 7, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by MechBFP\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dash8466","CreatedById":192905,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-07T18:48:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nmaybe but its hard to answer everything I would guess\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealKerbal3x","CreatedById":183830,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-07T18:51:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223595050\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557249374\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022106975\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Angel-125\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Angel-125 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah! I might make a version of my Mk1 Station Arm from KerbalActuators, which is currently a programmable single-part robot arm, and turn it into a multi-part robot arm powered by the DLC\u2019s Kerbal Robotics (or whatever it\u2019s called). Speaking of which, here\u2019s hoping that we get a sequencer of some sort. Like, record positions of various servo parts and then play them back. I did that for KA but a DLC powered solution would be one less thing that I have to maintain...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIIRC the new mechanics are coming in a free update alongside the DLC, so you won\u2019t need to have the DLC as a dependency for your mods.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223595105\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557254697\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022110814\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022klesh\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, klesh said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAre you guys planning on having another DLC release livestream featuring Scott Manley?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u2019d love it if they did that again! But since I live across the pond from you guys, it would probably end up being at an unholy time for me \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}